description: The demolition of existing buildings at Cannon Wharf Business Centre, 35 Evelyn Street SE8 and construction of buildings of 3 to 8 storeys plus two buildings 20 and 23 storeys in height, comprising 6,588m2 commercial units (Use Classes B1, A1, A2, A3, A5 & D1) and 679 residential units with on-site energy centre, 401 car parking spaces, cycle parking, and associated landscaping, with accesses onto Evelyn Street, Rainsborough Avenue and Yeoman Street.
